{"tid":2086543,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"淘仔耳機集中討論貼(49) -冇人開既喂","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T19:11:37.000Z","uid":33821,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"abd9e9064895980f84b18ed9419bbbdd10fcc442","tid":2086543,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZG9nEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZG9nEP.jpg&h=ec34624e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">新嚟嘅巴打可以先睇睇FAQ、常用簡稱，咁就可以快啲知道我地傾緊乜:</span><br />\n(例：日馬= 日本Amazon，唔係沙田賽馬早場&hellip;)<br />\n<br />\n近期熱門推介列表 / 其他淘寶店鋪 (Member Only):<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n高登/連登巴打耳機包膠集:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/BXWSv3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FBXWSv3&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=ba739f0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/BXWSv3</a><br />\n<br />\n就黎1001/差唔多1個月沉底搵人搵過個新POST<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZQUicP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZQUicP&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=ae819be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZQUicP</a><br />\n<br />\n***重要聲明***<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n1. 淘仔野有時可能會非常超值。但產品價格可升可跌，甚至變成毫無2手價。 <br />\n2. 買淘仔野未必一定能夠穩賺性價比，人地買到果把聲未必等於你聽到果把，耳機做功同聽感冇一定既保證，因為大多數冇QC就出貨， <br />\n3. 購買淘仔耳機可能會招致損失&mdash;&gt;寄返大陸走黎走去都係時間同錢。<br />\n<br />\n舊帖內有以下既耳機討論<br />\n<br />\n悅耳 :1圈4鐵,6單 <br />\n美樂城seek keep: diy se535 vs2 <br />\n聲菲爾音頻商城 : diy K3003 <br />\n值得逛逛 : diy 535四單終極調音版動鐵版<br />\n線材 小凡/發燒銀線坊<br />\n<br />\n舊Post合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=772cde61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n開Post格式<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZQUicP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZQUicP&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=ae819be9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZQUicP</a><br />\n<br />\n使用器材列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=716cce89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f15741355607095c6bd866308ef255f860a05e6","tid":2086543,"uid":5477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"聽日2pm 好想見到你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9LC2rC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9LC2rC.jpg&h=53c08f31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DqtQCZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDqtQCZY.jpg&h=2c2d4efa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7RhU4EZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RhU4EZ.jpg&h=e43f3802&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCa0fMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCa0fMF.jpg&h=47c379f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55Ajwj1.jpg\" dat